      Sort by Process Id

      Sort by up time, newest processes first
      static java.util.Comparator<OSProcess> OperatingSystem.ProcessSorting.UPTIME_DESC
      Sort by up time, oldest processes first
      static java.util.function.Predicate<OSProcess> OperatingSystem.ProcessFiltering.VALID_PROCESS
